Install virtual environment by running:
sudo apt install virtualenv

Create virtual environment named flask:
virtualenv flask

To activate virtual environment:
cd flask
source bin/activate

Next, install flask on virtual environment:
pip install flask

Install mysql connector:
pip install mysql-connector

mysql -u root -p
source setup.sql // this will create the database for you

cd to project directory and use the following command to run webpage
python 'classname'.py

**if you run into error 'no module named configparser':
pip install configparser****

To deactivate virtual environment:
deactivate

